                    <span>This is the best book an a Holocaust topic I have read, even though it troubled me greatly. I had always believed that the destruction of Europe's Jews was carefully planned, not largely improvised as Professor Browning demonstrates with blinding clarity and unassailable research. It does not diminish the evil but it helps to explain et. Do buy this powerfull book.</span>
                  
              
